新进警官的薪金不断下降，已经低至一年25,100美元。在数年激烈争吵过后，{{link-en|纽约市与巡警福利协会|Patrolmen's Benevolent Association of the City of New York}}于2008年8月21日达成四年的新协议。<ref>{{cite news | title=Deal Raises Officers’ Pay 4% a Year | date=2008-08-22 | publisher=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》 | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/22/nyregion/22pba.html | accessdate=2009-08-19 | archive-date=2021-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410093218/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/22/nyregion/22pba.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> 

该协议从2006年8月1日到2010年7月31日有效，决定在这四年中给警官17%的加薪，起薪则由$35,881提高到$41,975，最高薪金从一年$65,382上涨到约 $76,000。再加上工龄津贴、节假日补助、夜班奖金和其他福利，警官能拿到的最高收入达到了约$91,823（不含加班补助）。这也是自1994年以来，纽约市和巡警福利协会首次在没有仲裁人的情况下达成协议。<ref>[http://www.1010wins.com/NYPD-Officers-Get-17-Percent-Raises-over-Four-Year/2829313 NYPD Officers Get 17 Percent Raises over Four Years] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201054019/http://www.1010wins.com/NYPD-Officers-Get-17-Percent-Raises-over-Four-Year/2829313 |date=2008-12-01 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nyc.gov/portal/site/nycgov/menuitem.c0935b9a57bb4ef3daf2f1c701c789a0/index.jsp?pageID=mayor_press_release&catID=1194&doc_name=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nyc.gov%2Fhtml%2Fom%2Fhtml%2F2008b%2Fpr326-08.html&cc=unused1978&rc=1194&ndi=1 |title=Police Officer Contract Breakdown |access-date=2009-08-19 |archive-date=2020-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531025152/http://www.nyc.gov/portal/site/nycgov/menuitem.c0935b9a57bb4ef3daf2f1c701c789a0/index.jsp?pageID=mayor_press_release&catID=1194&doc_name=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nyc.gov%2Fhtml%2Fom%2Fhtml%2F2008b%2Fpr326-08.html&cc=unused1978&rc=1194&ndi=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

但即使比到期的旧协议有所改善，新协议中纽约市警察局的警官收入仍然低于其他临近的警局；在临近地区，新進警官的年薪約為50,000美元，而有資深警官则達100,000美元。<ref>{{cite news | title=2005 Duties, 1985 Pay | date=June 29, 2005 | publisher=New York Daily News | url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/local/story/323524p-276555c.html | accessdate=2009-08-19 | archive-date=2006-05-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060524062113/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/local/story/323524p-276555c.html | dead-url=yes }}</ref> 

